=== Verb ===
{{en-verb}}
# {{intransitive}} To pay [[attention]] to, to [[note]].
#: ''Please '''listen''' carefully to what I am about to say.''
# {{intransitive}} To [[wait]] for a [[sound]] as a [[signal]].
#: ''You should '''listen''' for the starting gun.''
# To [[obey]] [[oral]] instruction.
#: ''Good children '''listen''' to their parents.''
# To have a [[chat]] with someone, particularly a confidential one.

